## Development Setup

You will need [Node](https://nodejs.org/) version `4.1.x` or above installed.

Run `npm install electron -g` to install [electron](http://electron.atom.io/) globally.

Run `npm install` to install all dependencies.

Then run `npm start` to start Snips.

## Running Tests

Simply run `npm test`.

